visitor.symboltable

Class ClassTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • visitor.symboltable.SymbolTable
      • visitor.symboltable.ClassTable

  • public class ClassTable
extends SymbolTable
    Objects of this class represent a symbol table of a Minijava class. Note: Implementation includes no error handling
